Title: Found Around the Unbound
Description:
This Lamplighter is looking for his fellow Arathi. The foreman says he directed an Arathi shipwright to Freywold Village.

My superiors insist that Peacekeepers do not leave Dornogal... but per their orders, I must assist Kaerter. And to do that, I have no choice but to leave the city.

<Leif quickly hides a smile.>

It is decided then. If you are willing, please meet us at Freywold Village. Your continued aid would be appreciated.
ObjectivesText: Meet Peacekeeper Leif outside Freywold Village.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Peacekeeper Leif outside Freywold Village.
RewardText:
It seems the locals have taken issue with our foreign companion. I am attempting to defuse the situation as best I can.

But we have more pressing problems.
